The data chart given therein does not conform to the constitutional requirement which necessitated the exercise by the Government with respect to backwardness of the class, their representation in class or classes of posts in the services under the State and efficiency of administration (
Article 335
). It is also not clear that since how long these posts were not filled and whether they could not be taken up for consideration as back-log vacancies. In sub-para 3 of para 28 of the counter affidavit, the position of present short-listed backlog posts has been mentioned as 26618 which includes direct recruitment posts and promotional posts of groups A, B,C and D category. On the basis of said data, reservation could not have been provided in the matter of promotion.
